e,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "more evil"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "wrongdoing"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "than thou"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (K.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "h`*aA $ar~N mino *aAka", "text_ar": "هٰذَا شَرٌّ مِنْ ذَاكَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "This is worse,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "than that"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (Msb.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fulaAnN $ar~u Aln~aAsi", "text_ar": "فُلَانٌ شَرُّ النَّاسِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Such a one is the worst,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of mankind"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; (S;) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^a$ar~u", "text_ar": "اَشَرُّ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (S, Msb, K;) this latter being the original, (Mgh, Msb,) but rare, (K,) or bad, (S, K,) peculiar to the dial. of the Benoo-'Ámir, (Msb,) or unused. (Mgh.) The fem. [of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$ar~N", "text_ar": "شَرٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$ar~apN", "text_ar": "شَرَّةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", [like as the fem. of its contr.,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "xayorN", "text_ar": "خَيْرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "xayorapN", "text_ar": "خَيْرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ",] (K,) and (of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^a$ar~u", "text_ar": "اَشَرُّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", S, * or of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$ar~N", "text_ar": "شَرٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", which is used for"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^a$ar~u", "text_ar": "اَشَرُّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", Kr) ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$ur~aY", "text_ar": "شُرَّى", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"ki